u1edfng cho c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<\/h3>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1<\/th>\n<th style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">Chi ti\u1ebft<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">92 \u00d7 54 \u00d7 8mm (L\u00d7W\u00d7H)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">C\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">34g (bao g\u1ed3m pin)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">M\u00e0u s\u1eafc<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">Tr\u1eafng, \u0111en, x\u00e1m, \u0111\u1ecf, xanh l\u00e1<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">Nh\u1ef1a ABS<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Giao di\u1ec7n nh\u1eadp<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">15 n\u00fat<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Pin<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">2 x CR2032<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Th\u1eddi gian ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng pin<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">&gt;150 gi\u1edd<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Th\u1eddi gian ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">500 gi\u1edd<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u00f3ng RF<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 2.4G, giao th\u1ee9c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">S\u1ed1 k\u00eanh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">1 \u0111\u1ebfn 80 k\u00eanh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 46.6216%;\">Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.2973%;\">30m<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bo_thu_phat_song_innosmart_usb_receiver\"><\/span>B\u1ed9 thu ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng INNOSMART USB RECEIVER<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>B\u1ed9 thu ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng INNOSMART USB RECEIVER l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m INNOSMART. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n User ID v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt d\u1eef li\u1ec7u cao, thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y.<\/p>\n<h3>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng<\/h3>\n<p>INNOSMART USB RECEIVER cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n User ID \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p s\u1ed1 ID cho t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng v\u00e0 m\u00e3 code S\/N duy nh\u1ea5t, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt, thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e3 h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n d\u1eef li\u1ec7u, ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n vi\u1ec7c nghe l\u00e9n v\u00e0 b\u1ebb kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng tin. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 2 khu v\u1ef1c v\u1edbi 16 byte EEPROM.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng theo d\u00f5i k\u00eanh, gi\u00fap ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n xung \u0111\u1ed9t k\u00eanh v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n sang k\u00eanh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec5u v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100m v